text: Vyacheslav Mikhailovich Lebedev (; born 14 August 1943, died 23 February 2024) is a Russian lawyer and jurist. He has been the Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of Russia since 1991. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Russian lawyers Category:Politicians from Moscow Category:Judges
title: Vyacheslav Mikhailovich Lebedev
